data.description: Imagine stepping into a stunning 3 Bedroom, 2 Bath home that boast modern elegance. The spacious living area features an open floor plan, perfect for entertaining guests or spending quality time with family. The kitchen is equipped with Whirlpool SS appliances and WASHER AND DRYER! The main bedroom offers a complete retreat and the 2 additional bedrooms (split floor plan) provide ample space for family members or guests. Carpet in all the right places-Living room and bedrooms. 9' Ceilings, shelving in garage, ceiling fans, covered back patio. Lemon and Orange Tree in backyard. Dirt backyard allows for the Buyer's own design. Walk in shower master bath. Blinds throughout. Huge walk in closet in main bedroom. Separate toilet room. Partial view fence-greenbelt directly behind property
